videos.headline: Kent State RB uses defender to roll over into end zone
videos.description: Jo-El Shaw rolls over a defender into the end zone to keep himself from being downed at the 1-yard line, giving Kent State a 7-0 lead.

videos.headline: Kent State RB plows through defenders to take lead
videos.description: RB Woody Barrett takes a 10-yard carry up the middle, breaking tackles to give Kent State the 1-point advantage.
